  "title": "🎓 (NO EXP NEEDED) BRAND & SALES TRAINEE 🎓",
  "description": "<h2>❓ Just graduated and unsure how to start building real skills for your future?</h2><p>This role is designed for individuals who want to <strong>learn fast, gain confidence, and develop transferable skills</strong> in communication, sales, and leadership — even with no prior experience!</p><p><br /><strong>📌 Responsibilities</strong></p><p><ul><li>Represent clients in outreach and brand campaigns</li><li>Engage the public and build strong communication skills </li><li>Support sales initiatives and campaign execution</li><li>Learn how real-world marketing and business operations work</li></ul></p><p><br /><strong>🫡 Requirements</strong></p><p><ul><li>Willingness to learn and grow </li><li>Comfortable speaking to people (or eager to improve)</li><li>Positive, open-minded attitude</li><li>Fresh graduates / ORD personnel welcome</li></ul></p><p><br /><strong>❤️‍🔥 What We Offer</strong></p><p><ul><li>Full training & mentorship (no experience required) 🎓</li><li>Clear progression into leadership roles 🚀</li><li>Performance-based incentives 💰</li><li>Supportive and growth-focused environment</li></ul></p><p><br />📩 <strong>Start your career with skills that actually matter. </strong><br /><strong>APPLY NOW ‼️</strong></p>",
